STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Auberto EGIPCIACO, Defendant-Petitioner. C-815 September Term 2018
082555 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 4, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003746-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
